| Setting | Value | Notes |
|---------|-------|-------|
| **Frame Duration** | 7.5 ms, 10 ms | Shorter = lower latency, higher CPU |
| **Bitrate** | 64 kbps | Fixed for mSBC |
| **Sampling Rate** | 16 kHz | Voice quality |

